[4e060040-933f-4471-9c12-1d55c97103b9/Paper Draft]   | 
[4e060040-933f-4471-9c12-1d55c97103b9/Paper Draft]   | In addition to the previously mentioned features, spafe allows for
[4e060040-933f-4471-9c12-1d55c97103b9/Paper Draft]   | computing the following spectrograms: \textbf{Bark spectrogram},
[4e060040-933f-4471-9c12-1d55c97103b9/Paper Draft]   | \textbf{Cqt spectrogram}, \textbf{Erb spectrogram} and \textbf{Mel
[4e060040-933f-4471-9c12-1d55c97103b9/Paper Draft]   | spectrogram}.
